they can have a single

01:13:48.600 --> 01:13:52.410
login and password,
and a single file home that they

01:13:52.410 --> 01:13:54.680
can use to store all their files.

01:13:54.700 --> 01:13:58.290
So that when I go to the Mac machine,
I use that same login and password

01:13:58.400 --> 01:14:00.040
as I use on the Windows machine.

01:14:00.040 --> 01:14:05.480
All of my configuration information
is stored in that record.

01:14:05.480 --> 01:14:07.630
The manager only has to
manage it in one place,

01:14:07.630 --> 01:14:09.700
and the user can access
it from one place.

01:14:09.700 --> 01:14:12.410
Incredibly convenient.

